'''MARS-H'''（{{Lang-en|'''M'''odular '''A'''mbidextrous '''R'''ifle '''S'''ystem - '''H'''eavy}}，模組化雙邊操作步槍系統—重型）是一系列由[[路易斯機械與工具公司|路易斯機械與工具公司（LMT）]]生產的[[SR-25狙擊步槍|SR-25]]規格步槍，設計基於[[LMT_MARS-L步槍|MARS-L]]，最大特點為採用了'''模組化武器系統'''（{{Lang-en|'''M'''odular '''W'''eapon '''S'''ystem}}，簡稱MWS）系列一體式上機匣。曾配上類似SR-25的308MWS下機匣銷售，自2018年起改為配上新的MARS-H雙邊操作下機匣銷售。MARS-H上所有鋼製部件皆通過{{Link-en|磁粒檢測|Magnetic particle inspection}}。

== 歷史 ==
LMT在2003年推出了市場上首款真正一體式構造的MRP上機匣後<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Modular LMT MRP: The Rifle for Anything|url=http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/the-modular-lmt-mrp-the-rifle-for-anything/|accessdate=2021-02-08|author=Christopher R. Bartocci|date=2002-08-20|last=|format=|work=Small Arms Defense Journal|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208220508/http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/the-modular-lmt-mrp-the-rifle-for-anything/}}</ref>，開始研發MRP的全威力槍彈放大版。

2009年，[[英國軍隊|英軍]]與其他國家的軍隊一樣在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]遇上[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56 NATO]]步槍威力及射程不足的問題。因此在12月，[[英國國防部|英國國防部]]初步編列150萬[[英镑|英鎊]]作緊急作戰需求合約（{{Lang-en|Urgent Operational Requirements}}）的預算，以尋找一款7.62 NATO口徑，在500-800公尺能有效殺傷的步槍。LMT的LM308MWS在英軍的測試中擊敗了[[黑克勒-科赫|黑克勒-科赫]]的[[HK417自動步槍|HK417]]、[[埃斯塔勒国营工厂|FN]]的[[FN_SCAR突擊步槍|SCAR-H]]、Sabre Defence的XR-10、以及奈特軍械和Oberland Arms的產品，被採用為[[L129A1精確射手步槍|L129A1]]，並透過執法國際（{{Lang-en|Law Enforcement International}}）進口至英國<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Taking Back The Infantry Half-km: Britains L129A1|url=http://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/Taking-Back-The-Infantry-Half-km-Britains-L129A1-06426/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Defense Industry Daily staff|date=2010-06-08|last=|first=|format=|work=Defense Industry Daily|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330135722/https://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/Taking-Back-The-Infantry-Half-km-Britains-L129A1-06426/}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Sharpshooter: The UK’s New L129A1 7.62x51mm Rifle|url=http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/sharpshooter-the-uks-new-l129a1-7-62x51mm-rifle/|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Dan Shea|date=2012-01-11|last=|format=|work=Small Arms Defense Journal|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210180805/http://www.sadefensejournal.com/wp/sharpshooter-the-uks-new-l129a1-7-62x51mm-rifle/}}</ref><ref name=":22">{{Cite web|title=The Lewis Machine & Tool Sharpshooter System – The All-American Commercial Model|url=https://www.ammoland.com/2012/04/the-lewis-machine-tool-sharpshooter-system/|accessdate=2021-02-07|date=2012-04-25|last=Riehl|first=F.|work=AmmoLand.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302075851/https://www.ammoland.com/2012/04/the-lewis-machine-tool-sharpshooter-system/}}</ref>。每個八人小組將獲分配一把L129A1，當中三人會被訓練使用該步槍<ref>{{Cite web|title=British L129A1 sharpshooter rifle|url=https://armamentresearch.com/british-l129a1-sharpshooter-rifle/|accessdate=2021-02-10|author1=Ian McCollum|date=2017-03-20|author2=N.R. Jenzen-Jones|format=|work=Armament Research Services|publisher=|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127135524/https://armamentresearch.com/british-l129a1-sharpshooter-rifle/}}</ref>。

2011年10月，[[新西蘭陸軍|紐西蘭陸軍]]採用了設有全自動模式的LM308MWSA為[[精確射手步槍|精確射手步槍]]，並命名為DMW（{{Lang-en|'''D'''esignated '''M'''arksman '''W'''eapon}}，精確射手武器）

2018年1月，LMT在[[SHOT_Show|SHOT Show]]展出了新的MARS-H雙邊操作下機匣及採用[[M-LOK|M-LOK]]的MLKMWS上機匣<ref name=":7" />。

2018年12月，MARS-H獲選為[[愛沙尼亞國防軍|愛沙尼亞國防軍]]新的精確射手步槍<ref>{{Cite web|title=Estonian Rifle Trials: SIG, H&K & LMT Rifles In Running|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/04/05/estonian-rifle-trials-sig-hk-lmt-rifles-in-running/|accessdate=2021-02-08|author=Matthew Moss|date=2018-04-05|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118053045/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/04/05/estonian-rifle-trials-sig-hk-lmt-rifles-in-running/}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Estonia receives first batch of R20 Rahe automatic rifles|url=https://defence-blog.com/news/army/estonia-receives-first-batch-of-r20-rahe-automatic-rifles.html|accessdate=2021-02-09|author=Dylan Malyasov|date=2020-07-23|format=|work=defence-blog.com|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122072600/https://defence-blog.com/news/army/estonia-receives-first-batch-of-r20-rahe-automatic-rifles.html}}</ref>。愛沙尼亞國防軍採用的為16英吋槍管短行程活塞版本<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=LMT Defense Begins Rifle Deliveries to the Estonian Defense Force|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2020/10/28/lmt-defense-begins-rifle-deliveries-to-the-estonian-defense-force/|accessdate=2021-02-08|author=Matthew Moss|date=2020-10-28|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128234427/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2020/10/28/lmt-defense-begins-rifle-deliveries-to-the-estonian-defense-force/}}</ref>，並命名為R-20 L。R-20 L為MARS-H系列首次採用短行程活塞系統，愛沙尼亞選用短行程活塞的原因為擔憂直噴式系統排出的氣體會對士兵造成健康問題。

LMT參與了USSOCOM的中程氣動狙擊槍械（{{Lang-en|'''M'''id-'''R'''ange '''G'''as '''G'''un - '''S'''niper}}，簡稱MRGG-S）計劃及中程氣動突擊槍械（{{Lang-en|'''M'''id-'''R'''ange '''G'''as '''G'''un - '''A'''ssault}}，簡稱MRGG-A）計劃。為此LMT為MRGG-S及MRGG-A提交了6.5 CM槍械，分別為20英吋槍管的MARS-HS及14.5英吋槍管的MARS-HA。參與MRGG-S的MARS-H採用了新的MRP-H 15.5上機匣，而參與MRGG-A的MARS-H採用了新的加長上機匣（長度較MLKMWS長約半格M-LOK孔），並加上了復進助推器。目前MRGG-S僅剩LMT與LaRue競爭，MRGG-S最終獲勝步槍將在現有[[FN_SCAR-H_PR精確射手步槍|Mk 20]]壽命週期結束時逐漸取代Mk 20<ref>{{Cite web|title=USSOCOM Small Arms Update - 2019|url=https://soldiersystems.net/2019/06/05/ussocom-small-arms-update-2019/|accessdate=2021-03-08|date=2019-06-05|work=Soldier Systems Daily|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102094443/http://soldiersystems.net/2019/06/05/ussocom-small-arms-update-2019/}}</ref>。

